<title>伊朗“提出强烈抗议”，点名五个国家</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E6%97%B6%E6%8A%A5+%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E2%80%9C%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E5%BC%BA%E7%83%88%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E7%82%B9%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%AA%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%B6</link>
